data.description: Remarkable custom-built ranch home with so much to offer! You will be impressed with the unique floor plan which has the primary and 3 bedrooms on the main floor. Kitchen has quartz countertops, pantry, eating area and walk-out to a wonderful covered deck perfect for enjoying summer evenings or grilling out. The primary suite has a large walk-in closet and full bath. On the other end of the main floor you will find 3 bedrooms and a full bath. There is space galore in the huge basement where the rec room includes a wall of built-ins for storage, a home theatre area, and walk-out to backyard. The home theatre system is negotiable. A 3/4 bath and another room being used as an office has a large walk-in closet. (Window is just short of egress window requirements.) Located in the Millard School District and close to everything. So much to love about this one! Make your appointment for a personal showing today.
